<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>404 Not Found in UCC</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Refresh" content="30;https://www.ucc.ie/"/>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family:sans-serif;font-size:12pt;margin:2em;">
    <h1>Oh no 😱 the dreaded 404 Not Found </h1>
    <h2>What you were looking for isn’t here</h2>
    <p>Here are some possible reasons for it to be missing from this server (www.ucc.ie):</p>
    <ul>
      <li>it may be at another URI (web address) in UCC, <a style="text-decoration:none;color:blue;" href="https://www.ucc.ie/en/search/"><u>try a search</u> 🔎</a></li>
      <li>the URI (web address) may have been misspelled or mistyped ✐</li>
    </ul>
   <p><a style="text-decoration:none;color:blue;" href="https://www.ucc.ie/"><u>Go to the UCC homepage ➡</u></a></p>
  </body>
</html>

